quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Kiya hum nay tera seena nahi khol diya
  94,2,Aur tujh per say tera bojh hum ney utar diya
  94,3,Jiss nay teri peth tordi thi
  94,4,Aur hum nay tera zikar buland kerdiya
  94,5,Pus yaqenan mushkil kay sath asani hai
  94,6,By-shak mushkil kay sath asani hai
  94,7,Pus jab to farigh ho to ibadat mein mehnat ker
  94,8,Aur apney parwardigar hi ki tareef mein dil laga